column3: “Smooth smoke which produces a delightful, calm, focused feeling.”

“This strain kept me super focused throughout the entire length of it, while at the same time left me feeling very euphoric and content.  An all is right with the world" feeling.  This is one of my favorite strains.”"
“Although my first experiences with this strain were lacking in buzz intensity further doses seemed not to add to the buzz but multiply it. Resulting in a hard hitting socially condusive buzz.”
“good buzz, sticky buds, but it smells like the seafood counter at a supermarket. very briney”
